    "description": "希望更多热爱这类型游戏的朋友们可以参与到试玩并给出任何游戏反馈，大家的支持是我前进最大的动力！感谢！<br>《星际意志》交流QQ群：940828740<br><br><strong>六十个基础核心，上百个装备机组，上千个芯片，你可以自由组装飞船，俯视角双摇杆操作进行射击的生存Roguelike游戏！在科幻太空中探索，构建出你最强的战舰吧！</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071260/extras/3b6079ab51979b0dc12a9368d4eb9eb9.webp?t=1725637130\" width=616 height=57 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071260/extras/07cb8cad9ab30411e872173cedff22cb.poster.avif?t=1725637130\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071260/extras/07cb8cad9ab30411e872173cedff22cb.webm?t=1725637130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071260/extras/07cb8cad9ab30411e872173cedff22cb.mp4?t=1725637130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>第一步：选择一个“核心”作为你的基础角色<br>第二步：选择一个“机组”作为你的初始武器<br>第三部：选择一个星系进行探索</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071260/extras/6bfcc1cc2bcda6ac5b42a8de35e4a297.webp?t=1725637130\" width=616 height=57 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071260/extras/a0d6957066430ac71c22371d4c974890.poster.avif?t=1725637130\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071260/extras/a0d6957066430ac71c22371d4c974890.webm?t=1725637130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071260/extras/a0d6957066430ac71c22371d4c974890.mp4?t=1725637130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>游戏会在探索过程中，不断的收集新的“机组”或“芯片”<br>使用“机组”可以给你的战舰扩充武器提升战斗力<br>使用“芯片”则可以给你战舰提升各种能力</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071260/extras/1532ab555b228bb5c77b41b1e654b2ca.webp?t=1725637130\" width=616 height=57 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071260/extras/6c1d65a0a5767cd91b216f13ce157ac7.poster.avif?t=1725637130\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071260/extras/6c1d65a0a5767cd91b216f13ce157ac7.webm?t=1725637130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071260/extras/6c1d65a0a5767cd91b216f13ce157ac7.mp4?t=1725637130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>每个“核心”或“机组”最多拥有4个接口，当接口用完，则无法装备更多零件，但你也可以无限提升你的接口数量！<br>每一个“机组”都可以使用鼠标右键进行旋转，调整最佳的角度进行战斗</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071260/extras/aadaf45c111246590f31b20e3c2c8767.webp?t=1725637130\" width=616 height=57 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071260/extras/3d9f96d5f44ba7ba2c2a6892dec5088b.poster.avif?t=1725637130\" width=620 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071260/extras/3d9f96d5f44ba7ba2c2a6892dec5088b.webm?t=1725637130\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3071260/extras/3d9f96d5f44ba7ba2c2a6892dec5088b.mp4?t=1725637130\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>游戏的为双摇杆射击，通过键盘移动，鼠标瞄准敌人。当然有很多武器都是可以自动攻击或放置到场景中作为陷阱使用~</strong>",
